-- Texas May Issue the Most Drilling Permits Since 1985
-- B y   D a v i d   W e t h e
-- 2012-03-07T20:25:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-07/texas-may-issue-the-most-drilling-permits-since-1985-correct-.html
Texas  is on pace to issue the most
oil and natural-gas drilling permits since 1985, Barry
Smitherman, chairman of the Railroad Commission of Texas, said
today at CERAWeek, a Houston conference held by IHS Cambridge
Energy Research Associates.  The commission oversees oil and gas drilling permits in the
state.  To contact the reporter on this story:
